name: Halloween Party
description:
HI,

Whenever I think I want to quit and take another new opportunity, I wish I could have easily chosen that moment. But those pessimistic thoughts always come when I'm alone, sometimes it hurts. but thank God for creating many great chefs, bakers for creating extraordinary goodness to divert all our incorruptible madness, belonging to emotional anxiety. Just keep moving forward and keep going.

AND This is my last minting on October. 
see you on November.

warm regards,
Desh
